{"parents": [], "prev": null, "next": null, "title": "8. ZEIT ONLINE Jinja Coding Guidelines", "meta": null, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"zeit-online-jinja-coding-guidelines\">\n<h1>8. ZEIT ONLINE Jinja Coding Guidelines<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#zeit-online-jinja-coding-guidelines\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"indentation\">\n<h2>8.1. Indentation<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#indentation\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>Use 4 spaces to indent HTML tags and template blocks.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"whitespaces\">\n<h2>8.2. Whitespaces<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#whitespaces\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>Use <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://jinja.pocoo.org/docs/templates/#whitespace-control\">whitespace control</a>\nto strip whitespaces around or within control structures where needed.</p>\n<p>Always pad <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://jinja.pocoo.org/docs/templates/#list-of-control-structures\">control statements</a>\nand variables with 1 space before and after their braces::</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"n\">HTML</span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"n\">Django</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"o\">%</span> <span class=\"k\">for</span> <span class=\"n\">item</span> <span class=\"ow\">in</span> <span class=\"n\">container</span> <span class=\"o\">%</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">span</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">{{</span> <span class=\"n\">item</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">text</span> <span class=\"p\">}}</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"n\">span</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"o\">%</span> <span class=\"n\">endfor</span> <span class=\"o\">%</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n<p>Also add a 1 space padding to <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://jinja.pocoo.org/docs/templates/#filters\">filter</a> pipes::</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"p\">{{</span> <span class=\"n\">container</span> <span class=\"o\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">join</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;, &#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">}}</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"blank-lines\">\n<h2>8.3. Blank lines<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#blank-lines\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>There is <em>no</em> blank line at the top and exactly <em>one</em> at the end of a file.</p>\n<p>Use one blank line to separate semantic HTML sections and jinja blocks (i.e. macros).</p>\n<p>Import and extend statements should be grouped at the top of a document, with\none trailing blank line.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"line-length\">\n<h2>8.4. Line length<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#line-length\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>A strict maximum line length is not enforced, but try to avoid unnecessarily\nlong lines with multiple tags.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"assignments\">\n<h2>8.5. Assignments<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#assignments\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>Avoid assignments for cached properties and static attributes, like\n<code class=\"docutils literal notranslate\"><span class=\"pre\">{%</span> <span class=\"pre\">set</span> <span class=\"pre\">val</span> <span class=\"pre\">=</span> <span class=\"pre\">view.val</span> <span class=\"pre\">%}</span></code>. <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://jinja.pocoo.org/docs/templates/#assignments\">Assigning</a>\nreturn values of computationally heavy methods, however, is encouraged::</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"o\">%</span> <span class=\"nb\">set</span> <span class=\"n\">web</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">crawl_web</span><span class=\"p\">()</span> <span class=\"o\">%</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"comments\">\n<h2>8.6. Comments<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#comments\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>Use <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"http://jinja.pocoo.org/docs/templates/#comments\">jinja style comments</a>\ninstead of HTML comments to prevent them from rendering::</p>\n<div class=\"highlight-default notranslate\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"c1\"># TODO: This section needs to be reworked. #}</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"embedded-code\">\n<h2>8.7. Embedded code<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#embedded-code\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<p>Avoid substancial computation within control structures and try to move such\ncode to view properties.</p>\n<p>Still, code inside jinja control structures is <em>mostly</em> Python and should\nconform to <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008\">PEP8</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"]], "sourcename": "jinja/coding-guidelines.md.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">8. ZEIT ONLINE Jinja Coding Guidelines</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#indentation\">8.1. Indentation</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#whitespaces\">8.2. Whitespaces</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#blank-lines\">8.3. Blank lines</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#line-length\">8.4. Line length</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#assignments\">8.5. Assignments</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#comments\">8.6. Comments</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#embedded-code\">8.7. Embedded code</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": true, "page_source_suffix": ".md", "current_page_name": "jinja/coding-guidelines", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}